<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الْجِيم والذال والهمزة<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">جَأَذ يَجْأذ جَأْذا:</span> شرب،<span class="c5"> أنْشد أَبُو حنيفَة:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وجائذ فِي قَرقَفِ المُدَام<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>شُرْبَ الهِجَان الوُلَّه الهِيَامِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">[مقلوبه:</span> <span class="c2">(ذ أج)</span>]<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>ذَئِجَ من الشَّرَاب وذَأجَ يَذْأَجُ ذَأْجا،<span class="c5"> وذَأَجاً:</span> أَكثر.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">والذَّأج:</span> الشّرْب الشَّديد، عَن أبي حنيفَة،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>خوامِصاً يشربْن شُرْبا ذَأْجا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>لَا يَتَعَيَّفْنَ الأُجَاج المَأْجا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">وذَأَج السِّقَاءَ ذَأْجا:</span> خرقه.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">وذَأْجه ذأْجا:</span> نفخه.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وذَأَج النَّار ذأْجا،<span class="c5"> وذَأَجاً:</span> نفخها، وَقد رُوِيَ ذَلِك بِالْحَاء.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وذأجه ذَأْجا،<span class="c5"> وذَأَجاً:</span> قَتله، عَن كرَاع.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>الْجِيم والثاء والهمزة<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">جَئِث الرجل جَأَثاً:</span> ثقل عِنْد الْقيام أَو حمل شَيْء ثقيل.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وأجأثه الْحمل.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">وجَأَث الْبَعِير بِحمْلِهِ يَجْأَث:</span> مر بِهِ مُثقلًا، عَن ابْن الْأَعرَابِي.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c5">وجُئِث جَأْثا:</span> فزع.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c5">ورَجُل جَآث:</span> سيئ الْخلق.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c5">وانْجَأث النّخل:</span> انصرع.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span class="c5">وجُؤْثة:</span> قَبيلَة إِلَيْهَا نسب تَمِيم.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>